  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nThe following [PR](https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/5151) updates the `subscribedEventstream` bool flag to `true` in order to prevent from double subscribing of events. **Unfortunately, this causes the light client to not subscribe to any events at all**\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\n- The light client should subscribe **only once** to optimistic/finality updates\r\n\r\n**Steps to Reproduce**\r\n\r\n1. Run the light client and notice that the heads are not updated\r\n\r\n",
